<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weather App Homepage</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-image: url('/images/windows_xp_bliss-wide.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            min-height: 90vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        h1 {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            color: #e8811a;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .weather-form {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .form-text {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-text label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .form-text input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .radio-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .radio-option {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .get-weather {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #e8811a;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        p {
            text-align: center;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .note {
            color: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(4,12,103,1) 0%, rgba(33,22,22,1) 49%, rgba(0,212,255,1) 100%)
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Weather App ☀️</h1>
    <form method="GET" action="/weather" class="weather-form">
        <div class="form-text">
            <label for="city">Enter City Name</label>
            <input id="city" name="city" type="text" required placeholder="City Name">
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>Forecast Type</p>
            <div class="radio-group">
                <div class="radio-option">
                    <input type="radio" id="today" name="forecast" value="today">
                    <label for="today">Today</label>
                </div>
                <div class="radio-option">
                    <input type="radio" id="fiveday" name="forecast" value="fiveday">
                    <label for="fiveday">5-Day</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>Temperature Unit</p>
            <div class="radio-group">
                <div class="radio-option">
                    <input type="radio" id="fahrenheit" name="unit" value="imperial">
                    <label for="fahrenheit">Fahrenheit</label>
                </div>
                <div class="radio-option">
                    <input type="radio" id="celsius" name="unit" value="metric" checked>
                    <label for="celsius">Celsius</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="get-weather">Get Weather</button>
    </form>
    <footer>
        <p class="note">Thank you professor! I learned so much in this class. Have a great Spring Sem!</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>